经纪人假借婚恋名义诱导消费者到仲恺购房的现象。此类行为严重侵害购房人合法权益，扰乱原本健康有序的市场环境。此次发布通知，旨在厉打击此类违规销售行为，推进房地产市场乱象整治工作。惠州回应“30多名男子被女友‘刘佳’诱导买房”：共有15名女销售参与"},"attached_info":"CkII5OvX/oKKv+hxEAMaCTExMzk1ODM4NyDEzsu+BjAAOM0FQBtyCzE0ODg4OTQzODg3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"57 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-db3ab8b3f1138b78a5ac47397d58321e_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"28_1742015967.805481","card_id":"Q_14566594237","target":{"id":14566594237,"title":"在研究生复试的时候被问到「你是否有读博的打算？」该怎么回复比较妥当？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/14566594237","type":"question","created":1741578512,"answer_count":35,"follower_count":51,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3252,4287,19768,44476,88473],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkEI5OvX/oKKv+hxEAMaCTExMzg5MDA1MyCQwrm+BjAAODNAHHILMTQ1NjY1OTQyMzd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"57 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-23a48c5205252567500bb52d51981f86_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"29_1742015967.805900","card_id":"Q_14805302993","target":{"id":14805302993,"title":"该不该让孩子在限定的时间内玩手机？还是一下不让碰手机？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/14805302993","type":"question","created":1741792581,"answer_count":70,"follower_count":89,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1330021,2133163,2155525],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"孩子写完作业有时会要玩一会手机，10分钟或者半小时，该不该给？"},"attached_info":"CkEI5OvX/oKKv+hxEAMaCTExMzk0MDczOSDFysa+BjAAOFlAHXILMTQ4MDUzMDI5OTN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"57 万热度","trend":0,"debut":fal